metadata.description:
Does your child use or need a communication device?   Let their Yoto be their voice!
Your child can scroll through the emoji and push the button to "speak" what they need.  It does need to be fully downloaded to your player to work properly.
This card has a few phrases that are helpful around the home and to the use of Yoto.
